{"tid":793622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，最近開咗個伊甸園","createTime":"2018-08-25T14:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T18:34:06.000Z","uid":143774,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"23397fe5b7c88e25722a734b7f583280ba690b30","tid":793622,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"請咗兩條女嚟做下啲細藝，採下<del>陽</del>果實咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/222040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F222040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=992f2fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢地啲手藝有啲生疏<br />\n<br />\n屋企都請咗個工人姐姐，佢而家抺緊地，佢都幾鐘意乾淨，好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/222236_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F222236_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dba4394e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有隻奶牛，佢成日都痴線，要打鳩佢蘿友先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/222312_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F222312_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=13098e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗個農場點少得有泳池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，天口熱都可以泳下水，呢個係我嘅浮波，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我唔識游水的</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 萬一浸死咗就慘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/222544_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F222544_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0fbe4ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然點少得保安睇住個農場，費時失竊，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔見野真係好大鑊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/222802_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F222802_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2e08acd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/223028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F223028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ee089d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家參觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ec189f495e3962e5c1244d7363255e92df47f2","tid":793622,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d43b20e0d9e8d4bb5c6f9cededd27c54293041","tid":793622,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91ec189f495e3962e5c1244d7363255e92df47f2","tid":793622,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"質素